OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774795970
OL,3,C13-year-old girl and two others dead
OL,4,Cafter car hits tree in North
OL,5,CLincolnshire
OL,7,FEmergency services attended but the
OL,8,Fdriver, a 44-year-old man, a 48-year-
OL,9,Fold man who was sitting in the front,
OL,10,Fand a 13-year-old girl , who was
OL,11,Fsitting in the back were all
OL,12,Fpronounced deceased at the scene.
OL,14,FA police spokesperson said: "Their
OL,15,Ffamilies have been informed and are
OL,16,Fbeing supported by specially trained
OL,17,Fofficers at this incredibly difficult
OL,18,Ftime."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
