PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774795970
OL,3,C13-year-old girl and two others dead
OL,4,Cafter car hits tree in North
OL,5,CLincolnshire
OL,7,FA nine-year-old boy and a 15-year-old
OL,8,Fgirl were taken to hospital to receive
OL,9,Ftreatment for serious injuries. The
OL,10,Fgirl's injuries are being treated as
OL,11,Flife threatening.
OL,13,FPolice say they have begun
OL,14,Finvestigating the incident and are not
OL,15,Fyet sure why the car left the road.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
